.\" Manpage for Simple Shell
.TH HSH 1 "August 2025"
.SH NAME
hsh \- A Simple Shell
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
A simple shell that can run in interactive or non-interactive modes
.SH EXAMPLES
.B Interactive Mode:
.sp
$ ./hsh
.br
($) /bin/ls
.br
hsh main.c shell.c
.sp
.B Non-Interactive Mode
.sp
$ echo "/bin/ls" | ./hsh
.br
hsh main.c shell.c test_ls_2
.SH AUTHORS
- Hasanali Qadirov
.br
- Jamil Hajizade
